videos.headline: Utah State strikes first with 9-yard TD pass
videos.description: Jordan Love throws a back-shoulder pass to Jalen Green, who goes down to scoop it up in the end zone and give the Aggies a 7-0 lead over the Broncos.

videos.headline: Boise State responds with 2-yard TD run
videos.description: RB Alexander Mattison gets behind his blockers and powers his way across the goal line, capitalizing on the interception and tying the Aggies at 7-7.

videos.headline: Kaniho makes one-handed INT for Broncos
videos.description: Jordan Love tries to connect with Jalen Greene, but Kakaula Kaniho steps in front to make a one-handed interception, giving Boise State possession in Aggie territory.

videos.headline: RB Mattison hurdles defender to set up Boise State FG
videos.description: Alexander Mattison gets a head of steam and goes airborne over DJ Williams for a 13-yard gain to help set up the Broncos' go-ahead field goal.

videos.headline: Mattison runs in 2nd TD of first half
videos.description: Alexander Mattison muscles his way across the goal line for a 1-yard touchdown run, extending the Broncos' lead to 17-7 over the Aggies.

videos.headline: Aggies cut into lead with 12-yard TD pass
videos.description: Jordan Love puts up a back-shoulder throw to Ron'quavion Tarver, who makes the adjustment and brings it in to trim the Broncos' lead to 17-14.

videos.headline: Bright takes screen pass 83-yards for a TD
videos.description: Jordan Love dumps a pass off to Gerold Bright who goes 83-yards for a Utah State touchdown.
